{"tid":1346374,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港共和國宣布元朗事件定性為恐怖襲擊","createTime":"2019-07-22T04:02:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-22T09:46:19.000Z","uid":25434,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"bcf26f0aa4fc13dc903875537f6c57ebe4aec8b7","tid":1346374,"uid":25434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T04:02:55.000Z","msg":"就昨日（七月二十一日）晚上在元朗發生的暴力行為，香港共和國政府作以下回應：<br />\n<br />\n　　有白衫黑社會人士在元朗地鐵站一帶向市民連番暴力襲擊，包括用棍打人，用鐵通襲擊途人，亦破壞附近私家車，行為令人髮指。<br />\n<br />\n　　與此同時，腥港狗隻協助黑社會進行恐怖襲擊，政府嚴厲譴責狗隻毫無人性！<br />\n<br />\n        香港共和國定性事件為恐怖襲擊，並研究派出人手維拎元朗治安。<br />\n<br />\n　　香港作為法治社會完全不能容忍任何暴力行為，政府予以強烈譴責，並會嚴正追究。"},{"pid":"055970c70a77e9a0614a6be33e1e0e926b971cad","tid":1346374,"uid":25434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T04:03:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df784b254509f024d1c61576dedb0d2c70f8dddc","tid":1346374,"uid":248470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T06:37:53.000Z","msg":"建制派及其政府 公然向香港市民發動恐怖襲擊！<br />\n<br />\n地鐵故意堅持開住車箱門，任由警黑合作虐打市民<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香港政府= 台灣鄭捷"},{"pid":"994acf0cdec816381e2016286005b500742d8b8e","tid":1346374,"uid":248470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T09:40:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a802181bbe7987ea8e6a70abe0f59ab78872ca9e","tid":1346374,"uid":7736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T09:46:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}